23 January 2008Members of the media are reminded to submit details for accreditation for the State of the Nation Address (SONA), which will be on 8 February 2008.Journalists are requested to include the name of the media house that they represent, ID or passport number.The deadline for submission is today, 23 January 2008 at 16h00.Please send your details to:Ntombomzi Mbelebele Tel: 021 403 2242 Cell: 073 202 0078 E-mail: nmbelebele@parliament.gov.za ; orNolizwi Magwagwa Tel: 021 403 2465 Cell: 083 313 1323 E-mail: nmagwagwa@parliament.gov.zaIssued by: Government Communications (GCIS)